From 289d755bcbcd39e00cf77d1db956702213e57615 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Chen Tessler <ctessler@nvidia.com>
Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 09:46:19 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Add ProtoMotions BeyondMimic tracker policy

Adds support for deploying ProtoMotions BeyondMimic (BM) tracker
policies on the Unitree G1 via ONNX inference.

New files:
- g1_protomotions_bm_tracker_cfg.py: sim + real pipeline configs
- protomotions_bm_tracker_policy.py: ONNX policy with action history
  feedback, anchor-body rotation references, motion fade-in/fade-out
- protomotions_utils/: bundled motion playback and state derivation
  utilities from ProtoMotions (no protomotions install needed)

Modified files:
- g1_cfg.py: BM tracker DOF + body configs
- env_cfgs.py: virtual gantry spring-damper safety harness
- mujoco_env.py: FK body tracking, gantry forces, blend-in/blend-out
- rl_pipeline.py: motion callbacks, gantry lifecycle
- base_policy.py: post_step_callback / reset_alignment hooks
- __init__.py: register BM tracker policy
- run_pipeline.py: --onnx-path, --motion-path, --motion-index,
  --simulate-deploy, --prepare-seconds, --hold-seconds CLI args

Signed-off-by: Chen Tessler <ctessler@nvidia.com>
